doc.title: Amolladih mabul yasgaarawi fakim mayxaarah
doc.description:
Ta mayxaarah hayperlinki elle fakkiima inna meqennal lowsissuh koo xiqsissa.

Xangabu: gersi birooserwa, pop-up taagatak, qusba taagatak, qusba inkognito taagatak, awayih taagatak (default)

Tabs: gural yan tab, awayih tab, migdal tan tab ( sugtem)

Abnisso caalat: abbinoowele, tonnaak taamita (sugte)
